'remove:Remove a worktree' \
'r:Remove a worktree' \
'rm:Remove a worktree' \
'sync:Sync worktree with main (merge origin/main into current branch)' \
'sy:Sync worktree with main (merge origin/main into current branch)' \
'review:Review worktree changes vs main in neovim Diffview' \
'rev:Review worktree changes vs main in neovim Diffview' \
'main:Switch to the main branch tmux session' \
'ma:Switch to the main branch tmux session' \
'linear:Open the Linear issue for the current worktree' \
'li:Open the Linear issue for the current worktree' \
'git-hub:Open the GitHub PR for the current worktree (or create-PR page)' \
'gh:Open the GitHub PR for the current worktree (or create-PR page)' \
'completions:Generate shell completions' \
'hook:Handle Claude Code hook events (internal use)' \
'prune:Prune worktrees with merged PRs (pull workflow only)' \
